text: Natasha Henstridge (born August 15, 1974) is a Canadian model turned actress. She is best known for playing the extraterrestrial-human hybrid antagonist Sil in the 1995 science-fiction horror movie, Species, which was her movie debut. She played Lisa Rayborn in the 1998 comedy movie, You Lucky Dog. She also played Dawn in the television series, The Secret Circle. Henstridge was born in Newfoundland. She was raised in Fort McMurray, Alberta. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Alberta Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian television actors Category:People from Newfoundland and Labrador
